{
  "page": "Undergaoler",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>An <b>undergaoler</b> is a dungeon overseer.\n</p><p>In the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, there are supposed to be six undergaolers, but currently there are only three. Each undergaoler commands over gaolers and turnkeys, answering to the <a href=\"/index.php/Chief_undergaoler\" title=\"Chief undergaoler\">chief undergaoler</a> in turn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_undergaolers\">Known undergaolers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undergaoler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known undergaolers\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rugen\" title=\"Rugen\">Rugen</a>, an undergaoler in the Red Keep since the time of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. Actually a cover identity of <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>. Oversees the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_cells\" title=\"Black cells\">black cells</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undergaoler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Jaime I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403170108\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 170/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8572/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 698/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 34/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 797/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.674      1 -total\n 75.80%    5.059      2 Template:Ref\n 46.55%    3.107      2 Template:Ref/core\n 22.22%    1.483      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:20005-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403170108 and revision id 210096\n -->\n",
